        rdfs:comment        "Activation of the neurotrophin receptor NTRK2 (TRKB) by BDNF or NTF4 triggers downstream PLCgamma (PLCG1) signaling, resulting in formation of secondary messengers DAG and IP3 (Eide et al. 1996, Minichiello et al. 1998, McCarthy and Feinstein 1999, Yuen and Mobley 1999, Minichiello et al. 2002, Yamada et al. 2002)." ;
